Certainly! You can contact the New Jersey Legislative Ethics Committee at the following address and phone number:

New Jersey Legislative Ethics Committee
P.O. Box 068
Trenton, NJ 08625-0068
Phone: (609) 847-3905

You can also visit their official website at https://www.njleg.state.nj.us/ethics/ for more information and to submit a complaint or inquiry online.
